  geom_point(data = THOH, aes(x = id, y = imdb_rating, col = "")) +

- In general Treehouse of Horror (THOH) episodes seem to be on higher end of rating per season - THOH 31 is lowest, and lower even within the immediate range / season

get_season <- function(season_num) {
  tempDF <- simps %>% filter(season == season_num)
  return(tempDF)
}

s1 <- get_season(1)
